data.title: Dirk Jan de Geer
data.meta_description: Jonkheer Dirk Jan de Geer was a Dutch politician of the Christian Historical Union who served as Prime Minister of the Netherlands from 8 March 1926 until 10 August 1929 and from 10 August 1939 until 3 September 1940.
